<div class='p_profile_photo'>
<img alt="" src="/images/profile/missing-user-35.png?1339532938" />
</div>
<div class='p_comment_text'>
The biggest and best single tool you can use for going mouseless is AutoHotkey (<a href="http://www.autohotkey.com" rel="nofollow">http://www.autohotkey.com</a>).  It makes it easy to add extremely flexible hotkey support for any task you can dream up, even adding hotkeys to braind-dead apps like Outlook 2007.  It's the second thing I install on any coputer I use, and I feel absolutely crippled without ut.
</div>
